column51: company_description
Xoopit is an email organizational tool that enables users to retrieve meaningful content from their archived email.
One Block Off the Grid, a residential solar consultant, provides homeowners the option of comparing quotes from leading solar providers.
Appature offers enterprise marketing management software and web applications for the healthcare industry.
Action Engine is an agile software development, design and data services agency
Blackwave provides an integrated infrastructure platform for the storage and delivery of video over IP.
SoftLayer is a cloud-based infrastructure-as-a-service provider integrating physical and virtual devices of enterprises.
Mytopia develops cross-platform games that allow users on social networks to play with others via Android devices or iPads.
JackPot Rewards is an online retail portal providing shopping and sweepstakes loyalty programs.
Andigilog, a fabless analog and mixed-signal semiconductor company, provides intelligent thermal management solutions.
BARRX Medical, Inc. develops endoscopic treatment solutions for Barrett's esophagus and other chronic gastroenterological diseases
Power Analog Microelectronics designs and manufactures energy-saving analog and power integrated circuits.
Classiphix was an intelligent P2P commerce platform that used connectivity and confidence to provide safer online transactions.
StartupDigest provides a weekly email newsletter of the top tech and entrepreneurship events in the city to its members.
WiLinx Corporation is a semiconductor company providing single-chip complementary metal oxide semiconductor ultra-wide-band solutions.
Cohuman is a web-based collaboration and project management app that enables teams to coordinate and organize the tasks of their members.
Correlix offers real-time latency intelligence monitoring software for capital markets firms.
Redwood Systems provides LED lighting system architecture that enables customers to reduce energy costs.
OtherInbox is a company that builds technology to automatically organize emails enabling users to focus on messages based on their priority.
M-Factor develops web-based profit and revenue optimization software for the consumer goods, retail and restaurant sectors.
Athena Design Systems develops electronic design automation software, addressing the physical implementation challenges of IC design.

Kii (Formerly Servo Software) delivers a set of applications, APIs and SDKs to device manufacturers, mobile network operators, and end users, which help users to sync, search, and share mobile content on their and their friends' phones.
Levanta offers Linux management and data virtualization solutions to both private and government organizations.
EdgeSpring is a business intelligence platform providing visual analytics and business intelligence solutions.
DotSpots is a service enabling anyone to update news in real time with distributed objects of thought or 'dots.'
About.me is an online platform enabling users to create and maintain a curated page for self-expression.
Republic Project offers a cloud-based ad platform that makes it easy to scale campaigns, meet demand, and optimize performance in real time.
Hit Systems is a hosted IT company that provides IT systems and support for small- and medium-sized businesses.
Yamisee provided a live online learning platform for teachers and subject matter experts to share their knowledge.
Thinkfuse is a SaaS-based enterprise that allows companies to send regular progress reports to stakeholders.
Adobe Sign, formerly EchoSign is an e-signature and contract management company that helps its users get their documents signed online.
PI Corporation develops cloud-based software for personal information management and storage.
MoveableCode is a developer of location-aware fantasy games for mid-core gamers using Android and iOS platforms.
Daylife is a cloud-based media platform offering digital media management tools and content feeds to publishers and brand marketers.
Desktone offers a desktop virtualization platform facilitating the deployment of Windows desktops and apps from a cloud to end user devices.
Pulse is a news reading app that provides users with news from multiple RSS feeds on a single interface.
Opzi was a developer of social games for iOS and Android.
Standing Cloud provides app management services that facilitate cloud service providers in deploying and managing their apps.
Where I've Been is a personalized and interactive world map that lets users share their travels.
HipChat is a private group chat and IM network that provides real-time collaboration features for companies and teams.
ScaleIO develops ECS, a solution for data centers to cut storage costs and streamline storage operations.
GroupMe is a group mobile messaging service for finding, planning and purchasing group activities.
WeAre.Us is a California-based IT company providing a social support network.
KickFire, the leader in IP address intelligence, provides B2B firmographics based on IP address through its LIVE Leads, API and Prospector
Lifesize is a global innovator of video conferencing, collaboration, and meeting productivity solutions.
CHiL Semiconductor designs, develops and markets intelligent mixed-signal products using digital power techniques.
Aptana provides a web application development, deployment and management suite for users of Ajax, Ruby on Rails and PHP web technologies.
Enpirion is an analog semiconductor company offering highly integrated power management solutions.
RFinity develops person-to-person, cell phone-based payment and identification apps to facilitate financial transactions.
ecoATM is an e-waste recycling company. ecoATM kiosks evaluate and purchase used electronics from consumers for cash or store credit.
Adura Technologies develops enabling technologies for commercial building lighting control and energy management.
Rhythm sells and serves video, rich media and other immersive advertising formats to connect brand advertisers with mobile audiences.
Topsy, a social analytics company, provides instant answers to critical business questions via real-time analysis of public conversations.
Digit Wireless offers Fastap, a keypad technology solution that enhances handheld device features.
Silver Tail Systems employs web session intelligence and real-time behavioral analytics to detect and prevent fraud and abuse on websites.
Tatara Systems invents, develops and deploys convergence products for mobile operators and service providers.
Reliant Technologies, LLC develops aesthetic clinical solutions to rejuvenate aging and environmentally damaged skin.
Atrua Technology is a high-tech provider of intelligent touch control solutions.
Casabi provides a solution that enables carriers to deliver web-based content or services for cordless phones and other smart devices.
Peek made a simple smartphone. The software platform for smart apps on low-cost hardware is now part of Softbank, Viber and Twitter
Bluefin Labs is a social TV analytics company providing solutions to brand advertisers, advertising agencies and TV networks.
C2 Microsystems develops media processor devices for the broadband delivery of rich media content via internet and private networks.
GoPollGo is a real-time polling tool that lets brands and media properties collect and analyze feedback.
Multigig is a fabless, high performance analog and mixed-signal semiconductor company.
Ortiva offers mobile video optimization gateway, a server-based solution for the management of live and on-demand mobile videos.
Sometrics is a web platform for publishers to market free-to-play online games and monetize virtual currency via consumer destination sites.
Kima Labs is a startup that has developed their first mobile app, Barcode Hero.
Chronicity was a healthcare service provider for treating fibromyalgia, chronic fatigue syndrome, ADD/ADHD, and learning disabilities.
Whiskey Media develops topical websites that utilize the Django framework.
Jobfox is a job search and career networking site connecting job seekers with employers.
Natural Cleaners Colorado provides dry and wet cleaning services using carbon dioxide and green earth cleaning technologies.
Gaikai is a video game streaming platform that utilizes cloud-based gaming technology to enable users to play games instantly.
Blue Buzz Network provided online news.
Max-Viz designs, develops, and manufactures enhanced vision systems for the aviation industry.
Cotendo is a content delivery network and site acceleration services provider developing software focused on CDN technologies.
Particle Code develops a cross-platform that automates the porting process for software developers.
Flowgram allows sharing web pages, photos, and videos in a browser-based player that acts like an interactive screencast.
JavaJobs is an online job portal that offers IT- and Java-related job opportunities.
Behance is an online platform that enables creative professionals to showcase and discover creative work via online portfolios.
Locus mission is to help local businesses thrive.
Software intelligence to help DevSecOps teams across every industry tame cloud complexity and accelerate digital transformation
Socialbomb is a community platform connecting users mobile phones, blu-ray players, computers, and connected devices with others.
Imagine Communications provides digital video processing and edge multiplexing solutions.
Univa provides optimization and management software for traditional, dynamic and cloud data centers.
Tutorspree is an online platform that offers web based tuition services for the U.S students on various subjects.
OneRiot is a network of mobile apps that analyzes mobile social media activity to determine audience characteristics.
Moonshoot was a company that aimed to make English language learning fun for children by integrating it into online games.
ArcSight provides security and compliance management solutions that identify and mitigate business risk for enterprises.
AGEIA Technologies develops hardware-accelerated physics solutions for PC games.
U.S. Fiduciary is a financial firm offering a number of accounts-related services such as managed accounts, asset allocation and more.
Broadway Networks develops optical subsystems for broadband access applications. Acquired by Finisar.
Xelerated is a fabless semiconductor company proving HX devices that offer wire speed performance and other related services.
Oodle is a social marketplace offering customers a web and mobile app for buying and selling products.
The Climate Corporation is a technology platform helping people and businesses manage and adapt to climate change.
Kosmix is a search engine that allows users to perform advanced searches via multiple filters.
Xtify is an IBM company providing mobile app publishers with the tools to execute push and location-triggered notification campaigns.
Limerick BioPharma develops compounds which can be used adjunctively with marketed and investigational drugs.
iSkoot is an application that extends the reach of PC calling by allowing its users to make and receive PC calls using their cell phones.
Rudder is a financial management tool that enables users to separate and classify income and expenses.
Panvidea is engaged in the development and commercialization of entertainment and advertising content for various digital platforms.
Sway is a technology firm developing tools for global brands, small businesses, and marketing agencies.
TRAFFIQ is an end-to-end digital media planning and buying platform for advertisers, ad agencies and publishers.
Dexterra provides mobile platforms and apps that enable organizations to manage and optimize their mobile workforces.
CoTweet is a social media management and analytics tool enabling companies to adapt response-oriented customer service activities.
Reef Point Systems provides security solutions for converged wireless and wireline networks in the United States.
Paracor Medical is a medical device company providing technology-driven solutions for the treatment of heart failure.
Causata, a software company, develops and delivers software that connects and transforms customer data into portable real-time intelligence.
Asempra Technologies provides instant recovery solutions for Windows applications and data.
